+  Scenario: Tide entry with absent type field is silently skipped
+    Given the tide table for Fundy Cove with a tide entry missing the type field
+    When I ask for the next high tide after "2026-07-12T05:00:00Z"
+    Then the predicted high tide is at "2026-07-12T16:45:00Z" with height 4.5
+    # The entry missing type is silently skipped; no error is raised.
+    # Captain: is this intended behaviour or a data-validation gap?
